description: Creates a list. List is a set of input data for a variable in your event dataset. You use the input data in a rule that's associated with your detector. For more information, see Lists.

parameters.name: elements
parameters.description: The names of the elements, if providing. You can also create an empty list and add elements later using the UpdateList API. (string) ---

parameters.name: tags
parameters.description: A collection of the key and value pairs. (dict) --- A key and value pair. A tag key. A value assigned to a tag key.

nested_params.name: value
nested_params.description: A value assigned to a tag key.
